title: My Haunts
name: My Haunts
description:
A Map by Jacemachine

yadda yadda yadda...

properties.name: Bodega-Mart
properties.description: Posted by Jacemachine The Viking Food mart caters to the local neighborhood. It\'s not a real bodega, but they do sell glass pipes there next to their blunts and cigars.

properties.name: Chain Link Fence
properties.description: Posted by JacemachineI built this with two ignorant rednecks back in the spring of \'96. Pushing a wheel-barrow full of concrete through soft sand is fun. Really.

properties.name: Crab Island
properties.description: Posted by Jacemachinethe island isn\'t, but there is a constant party going on here when the sun shines. Sandbars allow easy boat-to-boat travel.

properties.name: Darth Tim's Gaming Lair
properties.description: Posted by JacemachinePrivate gaming haunt of mine, hosted at my buddy Tim\'s place. Actuvities that take place here are shrouded in dorkery. Tim like to cook meat and forcefeed it to us.

properties.name: Eat At Quiznos!!!
properties.description: Posted by Jacemachine And give my store some of your hard earned moneys. If you can tolerate "Mick\'s" attitude, you will LOVE our food!

properties.name: Frank's
properties.description: Posted by JacemachineYou know it!

properties.name: GAP
properties.description: Posted by Jacemachine I worked here for a while. It was the most boring job I\'ve worked at in a while.

properties.name: Hobos & Trolls
properties.description: Posted by JacemachineThe Brooks Bridge is a well known haunt of the local housing-impaired community. I\'ve been told there is a little living room set up down there, My friend recognized potted plants that had been stolen from the restaurant his mother owns.

properties.name: Lenny's Sub Shop
properties.description: Posted by Jacemachine  Yum! My favorite cold subs around! They also can do a pretty authentic Philly Cheesesteak, a must for a person with my background.

properties.name: McGuire's Pub
properties.description: Posted by Jacemachine Yum! A few of my friends refer to this as \'the Winchester\'-- This is where I took my Pop when he was down on vacation. I love their steak, and the Irishness doesn\'t hurt, me boyo!

properties.name: My Secret Lair HQ
properties.description: Posted by Jacemachine Actually, it\'s just my dingy apartment.

properties.name: The Monstrousity
properties.description: Posted by JacemachineA giagantic Condo structure complex withh soon to be attached shopping. It used to be a Fat Tuesday\'s that I used to Bounce at.

properties.name: Tourist Trash Drop
properties.description: Posted by JacemachineTourists drive slowly along The Island looking for places to park their SUV\'s, Minivans, and rental cars. %90 of the time, they choose poorly, and I get amusement by watching them get stuck. This area is littered with trash and empty bottles anywhere where people are known to wander. Thanks folks!
